    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like \"difficult days\" though. it feels like i'm actually poisoning them. just being in the house, the tension, the way i can't provide... it’s like i’m a weight around their necks. wouldn't it be easier if i just wasn't a factor anymore?",
