    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but they're constantly looking at me with such sadness. i see it in their eyes. i just feel like the most loving thing i could actually do for them is to stop being the reason they're unhappy. like, wouldn't they eventually be able to move on and find a better life if they didn't have to worry about me every single day?",
